":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T19:39:51.000Z","msg":"天生嘅<br />\nNeuroticism(容易唔開心)係一種性格特質<br />\n遺傳因素居多<br />\n無計<br />\n怪父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇吓self-help book <br />\n做吓運動<br />\n出面環境大起大跌嗰陣 由得佢<br />\n唔係自己錯 就唔好怪自己<br />\nMeditate吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉吓環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2b358fa400337dc23a2072e70000c347374001","tid":2295160,"uid":245484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T19:47:40.000Z","msg":"你會唔會開post 講<br />\n<span class=\"red\">有冇人耐唔耐就好開心，可唔可以分享下點樣令自己抑鬱啲?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有喜怒哀樂有咩問題,月都有陰晴圓缺啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚比d 不負責任既濕鳩正能量撚老點, 以為人一定要keep 住開心得嫁<br />\n長期都只有正面/只有負面都係病<br />\n你呢d&quot;耐唔耐&quot;抑鬱 ,即係情緒時好時壞, 就叫做正常<br />\n明白? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac4fbbe273653586c3d530ac513ab65d3d4dd27","tid":2295160,"uid":383941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T20:10:42.000Z","msg":"留個名先<br />\n好同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我以為得我一個係咁<br />\n本人份人好hyper<br />\n但有幾日就會灰到唔想見任何人<br />\n想收埋自己係房<br />\n係咁諗點解自己咁垃圾咁無用果啲<br />\n但其實我知自己人生已經好豐盛 生活好幸福"},{"pid":"a476f6fd74c07d3be81a388142d90b7884d37ba7","tid":2295160,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"暫時只係諗到食藥，真係有d幫助既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa32434148494ffc60ee8e871b4c735a1a33be9","tid":2295160,"uid":23431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n會一個人攤足一日<br />\n突然會想喊 覺得自己好孤獨"},{"pid":"3832fa1047be173570a254478d59b81704c1469e","tid":2295160,"uid":369795,"like":0,"dislike":0,